Upcountry Árnessýsla.title: Upcountry Árnessýsla
Upcountry Árnessýsla.byline: Upcountry Árnessýsla, or Uppsveitir Árnessýslu in Icelandic, is a rural area in South Iceland, home to many of the country's most famous attractions.

Upcountry South Carolina.title: Upcountry South Carolina
Upcountry South Carolina.byline: Upcountry South Carolina, also known as The Upstate, consists of the northwestern corner of the state.
